---
title: Indian Potato Chickpea Patties & Haloumi with Radish Salad, Garlic Dip & Apricot Sauce
description: A veggie patty can be packed full with a variety of nutritious surprises. These ones have chickpeas and golden potatoes seasoned with our Mumbai spice blend to add a zap of flavour. Don’t forget to drizzle over the sweet apricot sauce to make those veggie patties glow on the plate.
